title: Walk everywhere! Charming home with brand new garage, great neighbors
posting_body: ['Amazing rental opportunity in one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in the Twin Cities.', 'This charming single family home for rent is just blocks off Mainstreet…walkable to grocery store, restaurants, elementary schools, theater, parks, bike trails, and more.', 'Home has two bath, with two formal bedrooms upstairs and the possibility of a third on the main floor.', 'Large two car garage with storage.', '1,600 square feet.', 'Washer and dryer included.', 'Exceptional close-knit community with great neighbors!', 'Background, credit check, and income verification required.', 'Tenant is responsible for all utilities and snow removal.', 'Year long lease required.', 'Available October 1.']
